snippet.title: Star Wars - X-Wing - Gameplay
snippet.description:
JonTron literally stole the entire video without asking me for permission. Just because this channel is old doesn't mean I don't notice that shit. That's how you get popular kids, steal your shit from others!

Playing a "bonus" mission from X-Wing (1993).

You will see differences between X-Wing and later games like Tie-Fighter. There is no 3D model in your targeting computer and also when you target an enemy it only glows red for a short time. This made it a "little" difficult for me to find gunboats to kill.

This is from the "Collectors Edition" with digital voices. I had to quit right at that point, youtube´s 11 minute limit ... ya know.
